    <content>&lt;P&gt;I can confirm the issue:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P class=""&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;2024-11-24T10:29:26.33+0100 [API/20] ERR Failed to stage build: found no compatible cell with placement tag "trial"&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P class=""&gt;when I try to deploy&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://github.com/SAP-samples/cap-sflight" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;https://github.com/SAP-samples/cap-sflight&lt;/A&gt;. It's a freshly created Trial acocunt in the Extension Landscape&amp;nbsp;us10-002 (&lt;A href="https://api.cf.us10-002.hana.ondemand.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;https://api.cf.us10-002.hana.ondemand.com&lt;/A&gt;). Seems someone forgot to do the needed setup for trial in this CF landscape.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P class=""&gt;The CF Coding is:&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://github.com/cloudfoundry/auction/blob/main/auctiontypes/types.go#L27" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;https://github.com/cloudfoundry/auction/blob/main/auctiontypes/types.go#L27&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P class=""&gt;Maybe&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/139"&gt;@thomas_jung&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;can trigger the right people?&lt;/P&gt;</content>
